description: Price Improvement!!! Luxury Living on the River – Designer Condo in the Coveted Lido at Mission Valley  Welcome to your dream retreat in the heart of Mission Valley! This beautifully upgraded 2-bedroom condo in the exclusive Lido community offers modern luxury with resort-style amenities.  Enjoy an open-concept layout with high ceilings, designer lighting, and a stylish mix of slate tile, cherry-toned vinyl wood, and plush carpet. The expanded chef’s kitchen features DEKTON countertops, custom cabinetry, a farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances, and a gas range—perfect for entertaining or everyday elegance.  The versatile second bedroom works beautifully as a guest room, nursery, or office. The spacious primary suite boasts serene San Diego River views, a custom walk-in closet, and direct access to a dual-entry bathroom.  Relax on your private patio overlooking tranquil riverfront scenery. Additional perks include in-unit laundry, central A/C and heat, a gated parking space, and two storage lockers.  Lido offers premium amenities: two pools/spas, fire pits, BBQ areas, a clubhouse, gym, and direct access to river trails. All just minutes from Fashion Valley Mall, Trader Joe’s, top dining, Target, freeways, and the trolley.  Turnkey, stylish, and superbly located—this is Mission Valley living at its best. You won't find another like it! Luxury Living on the River – Designer Condo in the Coveted Lido at Mission Valley  Welcome to your dream retreat in the heart of Mission Valley! This exquisitely upgraded 2-bedroom condo in the exclusive Lido community blends upscale finishes with resort-style amenities for the ultimate in modern luxury.  Step into a stunning, open-concept living space featuring high ceilings, designer lighting, and a rich blend of slate tile, cherry-toned vinyl wood, and plush bedroom carpeting. The expanded chef’s kitchen is a showstopper—outfitted with striking DEKTON countertops, custom cabinetry, a farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances, a gas range, and sleek finishes fit for a culinary artist.  The versatile second bedroom—with its own closet—is perfect as a guest room, home office, or nursery. The spacious primary suite offers a serene escape with tranquil views of the San Diego River, a custom walk-in closet, and private access to a beautifully remodeled dual-entry bathroom.  Step out onto your private patio to take in peaceful riverfront views—your own slice of nature just moments from the city.  Additional perks include in-unit laundry, central A/C and heat, a gated assigned parking space, and two storage lockers. Lido residents enjoy top-tier amenities: two sparkling pools and spas, outdoor fire pits and BBQs, a stylish clubhouse, full fitness center, and direct access to scenic river trails.  Just minutes from Fashion Valley Mall, Trader Joe’s, top dining, Target, and major freeways & trolley stops, this turnkey gem is ideal for professionals, first-time buyers, investors, or anyone craving upscale convenience with a resort-style flair.  Luxury, location, and lifestyle—this is Mission Valley living at its finest. Don’t miss your chance to call it home.

priceHistory.source: Christine LaBounty, Realtor with Keller Williams Carmel Valley
